               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; name of the protagonist; a few lines on the incipit page of Text II; incipit of Text III; incipits of miracles and their numbers; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.&#xD;
